# Documentation Rules

Markdown must preview in standard viewers.

Docs must include:
- source coverage matrix
- legal/risk matrix
- database structure
- app page structure
- agent setup instructions
- numbered roadmap
- acceptance gates
- Mermaid block diagram source

DOCX/PDF export should render the diagram as an image when export tooling is available.
